extends ../ui_layout

block content
  .ui.container
    .ui.raised.segment
      .ui.ribbon.label
        h4(style="float:left")
          i.exclamation.triangle.yellow.icon
          | These were the fake news posts in the timeline. How many did you notice?
      br
      br
      .ui.three.cards
        
        .ui.fluid.card.dim()#card1
          .content
            .right.floated.meta 20 minutes ago  
            a(href='/user/zoe.g._')
              img.ui.avatar.image(src='/profile_pictures/user70.JPG')
              span Zoe Goodall
          .img.post
            img.transition.visible(src='/fakenews1.png', data-src='/fakenews1.png', onclick='openPost()', style='max-width: 100%; cursor: pointer;display: inline !important;')
          #info_5cc1c80765d61363b8a66544.read.rounded.right.floated.info_button(data-info_text="Real facts.com is THE news source for you. Learn about everything that's going on everywhere in real time. You can trust us!", style='z-index:12;text-align:center;align-self:flex-end;position:relative;bottom:10px;width:7%;height:auto')
            i.info.icon
          .content
            .description
              | Breaking News: Driving age just lowered to 12. DMV flooded with road test appointments and car companies cannot keep their newest models off the road.
    
      
        .ui.fluid.card.dim()#card2
          .content
            .right.floated.meta 30 minutes ago
            a(href='/user/k.r.h345')
              img.ui.avatar.image(src='/profile_pictures/user15.jpg')
              span Keith Hernandez
          .img.post
            img.transition.visible(src='/fakenews2.png', data-src='/fakenews2.png', onclick='openPost()', style='max-width: 100%; cursor: pointer;display: inline !important;')
          #info_5cc1c80765d61363b8a664e1.read.rounded.right.floated.info_button(data-info_text="ScienceTruth is everyone's favorite and reliable source for science facts.", style='z-index:12;text-align:center;align-self:flex-end;position:relative;bottom:10px;width:7%;height:auto')
            i.info.icon
          .content
            .description
              | Craving a donut? Think again! Scientists found that donuts are the leading cause of cancer in young children ðŸ˜³


        .ui.fluid.card.dim()#card3
          .content
            .right.floated.meta 1 hour ago
            a(href='/user/aperson')
              img.ui.avatar.image(src='/profile_pictures/user43.png')
              span My Name
          .img.post
            img.transition.visible(src='/fakenews3.png', data-src='/fakenews4.png', style='max-width: 100%;display: inline !important;')
          .content
            .description
              | 76-year old Janet Logan was arrested this morning, for allegedly training numerous chickens to attack her former husband. lol!
 
 

    br
    h3 Did you notice any signs of fake news in these posts?
    .ui.form
      .inline.fields
        label(for='help', style="font-size:120%;") They had clickbait headlines and wild images ?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', value="yes", name='help', tabindex='0')
            label Yes
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', value="no", name='help', tabindex='0')
            label No
    .ui.form
      .inline.fields
        label(for='like', style="font-size:120%;") They had spelling mistakes or dramatic punctuation ?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0')
            label Yes
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0')
            label No
    .ui.form
      .inline.fields
        label(for='write', style="font-size:120%;") They were from a suspicious website ?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='write',  tabindex='0')
            label Yes
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='write', tabindex='0')
            label No


    br
    h3 Tell us what you would do next to check the credibility of the above articles.
    .ui.form
      .inline.fields
        label(for='help', style="font-size:120%;") I would read the full article.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', value="yes", name='help', tabindex='0')
            label Yes
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', value="no", name='help', tabindex='0')
            label No
    .ui.form
      .inline.fields
        label(for='like', style="font-size:120%;") I would check the source.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0')
            label Yes
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0')
            label No
    .ui.form
      .inline.fields
        label(for='write', style="font-size:120%;") I would find corroboration from other credible sources.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='write',  tabindex='0')
            label Yes
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='write', tabindex='0')
            label No            
      
      .field
        label(style="font-size:120%;") What are the benefits and drawbacks of getting news on social media ?
        textarea(rows='2')

    br
    //-h3 Why is it important for people to act against cyberbullying?
    .ui.form
      .field
        label(style="font-size:120%;") Why is it important to evaluate the information you see on social media ?
        textarea(rows='2')
    br
    //-h3 What will you do in the future to be an upstander if you see cyberbullying?
    .ui.form
      .field
        label(style="font-size:120%;") What would you do in the future on real social media sites to make sure that the information you see is credible?
        textarea(rows='2')
    br
    .ui.big.green.labeled.icon.button.cyberbullying_end
          i.rocket.icon
          |   Finish Lesson

      
block scripts
  script().
    setTimeout(function(){
      $('.ui.ribbon.label').transition('bounce');        
    }, 1000);


    setTimeout(function(){
      $('#card1,#card2,#card3').transition({
      animation : 'jiggle',
      duration  : 800,
      interval  : 200
      });    
    }, 2000);


